# run_20260430_213933: Phase 2 LS sweep cell 1, combo A nosides + LS=0.0, 80ep. S2 best (top min 0.404). Hypothesis (LS=0.0 lifts wrist_smash) not supported: vs LS=0.1 baseline run_20260430_170325, head metrics flat, mean wrist_smash -1.6 pp, best-of-run wrist_smash -5.5 pp.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260430_213933/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260501_073430: Phase 2 LS sweep cell 2, combo A nosides + LS=0.15, 80ep. S3 best (top macro 0.753, top min 0.448, top acc 0.773). Vs LS=0.1 baseline run_20260430_170325, head metrics flat (+0.005 macro mean), mean wrist_smash +4.2 pp, range tightens 0.159 -> 0.066.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_073430/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_3.pt
